<title>VAILAMTAH VAN LAM A SI CH325</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Vancung khua vailam-tah lam in kal a herh, Hi hlei lam dang a um lo. A
 Ceumi Kutka ka phan bal lai lo, Vailam-tah lam zulh lo ahcun.

[C1]
   Vailam-tah van lam a si, (a si) Vailam-tah van lam a si (a si)
   Keimah zulh awkah lunglawmhnak a si, Vailam-tah van lam a si.

[V2]
 Thi thehmi lam kha keimah kal awk a herh, Khamhtu a kal cangnak lam. A
 cung sannak khua kha ka kai ahcun, Pathian he ka thlarau a um.

[C2]
   Vailam-tah van lam a si, (a si) Vailam-tah van lam a si (a si)
   Keimah zulh awkah lunglawmhnak a si, Vailam-tah van lam a si.

[V3]
 Hi vawlei cung in keimah ka kal cang lai, Zeitik hmanh kir ti loin. Ka
 inn ka kawl, Bawipa nih &quot;Ra!&quot; a ti, Khi innka in a ka hngah ko.

[C3]
   Vailam-tah van lam a si, (a si) Vailam-tah van lam a si (a si)
   Keimah zulh awkah lunglawmhnak a si, Vailam-tah van lam a si.</lyrics>
<key>Ab</key>
</song>